
Introduction
-------------
sententia helps you perform polls/surveys even in (near) real time to quickly find
out the options of a crowd, be it a mentometer in an auditorium or an intranet poll. 
Based on an API to enable other your own applications to access simple web interface

This is work in progress to at least initially experiment with concurrency technologies
on web and backend.




Development
---------------
Make sure you have environment setup, follow tips in http://devcenter.heroku.com/articles/scala